snippet.title: Gambit: Le Diable Blanc | Character Reveal | Marvel Rivals
snippet.description:
Every card he plays changes the game.

Remy LeBeau - better known as Gambit - has always been more than a charming thief. His Mutant gift lets him charge any object with explosive kinetic energy, but it's his wit and finesse that make him truly dangerous.

After the Timestream Entanglement tore apart his wedding with Rogue, Gambit struck a deal with the Grandmaster himself: steal a priceless contract from the Collector, and receive Chronovium dice that could be forged into new wedding rings.

Under the guise of an intergalactic honeymoon, Remy sets off on the ultimate heist - one that will spiral into cosmic chaos far beyond his wildest dreams.

Season 5 begins on November 14 UTC!

Deal the cards. Play the odds. Steal the show!
